Mentoda. I just watched Tyson's part again. Despite his speech problem, nothing he says gets bleeped. I do have to say that on the TV version he told Jeff Ross to "Suck on a fuckin' exhaust" but with his speech problem they bleeped suck and fuckin' because they both sounded the same. Also, snatch wasn't bleeped on the TV Version and it is cum, not come.
Cum is a bastardization of the word come to distinguish context, but come is also proper. Read Cujo.
